#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-getting-started.php:32
msgid ""
"Once you are familiar with how Bricks works its a good idea to learn about "
"templates. This is how you create your website header, footer and any other "
"type of reuseable content such as blog post layouts, archives, your search "
"result and error pages."
msgstr ""
"Kapag pamilyar ka na sa kung paano gumagana ang Bricks, magandang ideya na "
"pag-aralan ang tungkol sa mga template. Ito ang paraan kung paano ka lumikha "
"ng header, footer, at anumang iba pang uri ng muling magagamit na nilalaman "
"ng iyong website tulad ng mga layout ng blog post, archives, resulta ng "
"iyong paghahanap at mga pahina ng error."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-getting-started.php:36
msgid ""
"The \"Features\" articles covers topics such as the Unsplash integration, "
"custom code (CSS & JS), gradients, sidebars, shape dividers, global "
"elements, etc."
msgstr ""
"Ang mga artikulo sa \"Features\" ay sumasaklaw sa mga paksa tulad ng "
"integrasyon ng Unsplash, custom na code (CSS & JS), mga gradient, sidebars, "
"shape dividers, global elements, atbp."

